Package epfl.lsr.bachelor.project.store

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    KeyValueStore
    Abstract super-class of the different types of implementations for the KV-store
    KeyValueStoreForSingleThreadedArchitecture
    Implementation of a KV-store that should be used only with a single-threaded architecture, otherwise this will not ensure any kind of synchronization
    KeyValueStoreWithGlobalLock
    Implementation of a KV-store that should be used with a multi-threaded architecture.
    KeyValueStoreWithKeyLocks
    Implementation of a KV-store that should be used with a multi-threaded architecture.
    KeyValueStoreWithMapLocks
    Implementation of a KV-store that should be used with a multi-threaded architecture.
    ReaderWriterHelper<T>
    This class is used to nicely implement the readers-writer problem without any priority
